question: Find the first 3 people who have the role of CEO in more than one organization.
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)-[:HAS_CEO]->(o:Organization)
WITH p, count(o) as num_ceo_roles
WHERE num_ceo_roles > 1
RETURN p.name as person, num_ceo_roles as number_of_ceo_roles
ORDER BY num_ceo_roles DESC
LIMIT 3

question: Identify the top 3 countries with the most organizations in the 'Electronic Products Manufacturers' category.

question: Identify the first 3 organizations that have the same investor and are based in 'Italy'.
cypher:
MATCH (o1:Organization)-[:HAS_INVESTOR]->(investor)<-[:HAS_INVESTOR]-(o2:Organization)
WHERE o1 <> o2 AND o1.id < o2.id

RETURN o1.name AS org1, o2.name AS org2, investor.name AS investor
LIMIT 3

question: Name the organizations with the most board members who are also CEOs of other organizations.

LIMIT 10
